{"tid":1883352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約前市長彭博據報考慮拉攏希拉莉 大選挑戰特朗普","createTime":"2020-02-17T01:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T13:17:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"47ac8bda135dc7db29ef86190c1c75ab040e5f3c","tid":1883352,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:24:09.000Z","msg":"紐約前市長彭博(Michael Bloomberg)近日在民主黨初選支持度急升，據報考慮拉攏前國務卿希拉莉(Hillary Clinton)當副手，迎戰尋求連任的美國總統特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n彭博競選團隊消息稱，內部民調顯示，彭博夥拍希拉莉將是對抗特朗普的強大力量，有望在總統選舉力壓對方。彭博並沒有參與艾奧瓦州及新罕布什爾州的民主黨初選。<br />\n<br />\n希拉莉在2016年總統選舉獲得彭博支持，但她落敗後曾一再表示不會再參選。她早前在訪問中被問到會否考慮以副總統身份競逐，說這不會發生，卻又稱永不說不。<br />\n<br />\n根據民主黨初選民調，彭博及國會參議員桑德斯(Bernie Sanders)的支持率，力壓前副總統拜登(Joe Biden)，彭博在佛羅里達州民意領先。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2379276/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2379276%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=d452a010\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2379276/</a>"},{"pid":"57df536d76897b5bf00c54fdda3c0b9608a422ee","tid":1883352,"uid":155095,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:35:05.000Z","msg":"希拉里 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/229724/org/e82ca02fb670d057ede99c2ea0b3f4b2.JPG/S3Ogmwc4uLHl1-oE5FJ_5JWDsfmQjCPQJmd8KSZnfCk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F229724%2Forg%2Fe82ca02fb670d057ede99c2ea0b3f4b2.JPG%2FS3Ogmwc4uLHl1-oE5FJ_5JWDsfmQjCPQJmd8KSZnfCk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2e4b3784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1b9aaf96912feeddd1f306923ea1c74af9a6dc0","tid":1883352,"uid":191926,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:36:10.000Z","msg":"彭博都係奶共派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229c330df1003a2188057538e13c4982d